Bitmit is a Ebay like bitcoin shopping platform on which people from all over the world can trade their goods.

##History
Bitmit started in September 2011. (2.1).

##Features

* Buy now / auction
* Couple price to a fix usd/eur value
* Escrow service
* ID verification system
* Rating system
[(1)](https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=41592.0).
